description:
Volume 2 of the Technical Content Grimoire is coming to Unreal Fest Stockholm, presented by Tomislav Božić 📖

As both a Lighting Artist and a Technical Artist, Tomislav defined content pipelines and helps develop tools for content authoring. He'll be sharing that knowledge at Unreal Fest Stockholm in September!
title: Unreal Fest Stockholm Meet the Presenter: Tomislav
